name: Dreamy Undersea World
description: DUW is the abbreviation of the chain game Dreamy Undersea World, which is also the circulating token in DUW game.Dreamy Undersea World, as a cross-year sincere chain game masterpiece, is casual chain game that combines entertaining, playable and fun with super double destruction deflation, and is committed to enriching the Web3.0 and GameFi2.0 game ecosystem.
